title: Things you NEED to know about Typescript (#1 - The basics)

media:group.media:title: Things you NEED to know about Typescript (#1 - The basics)
media:group.media:description:
This is the first video of our Typescript video series, in which we want to give you an introduction into typescript - "from zero to hero". There will be more videos coming soon, where we dive a bit deeper into the language. This first one sets you up with a project, so you can enjoy writing typescript.

The second video of this series is not yet done, so please be patient :)
